channel.title: [Release] Fire-Isle Client/Source
channel.description:
[center]Fire-Isle Client+Server[/center] [center]Yup I have quit RSPS I have too much to do in real life now, It was fun while it lasted but I have much better things too do.[/center]
How Fire-Isle started, well a year ago I had a server called Fire-Isle, and it was great we were #4 on the top list and had over 200+ players. Then my Co-Owner stole my source and took it for himself and I got left with nothing so yeah. It sucked met a lot of cool people through this journey and I still talk to them and they are sorry for what happened.
Yes I'm not proud of this source I could make it 100times better if I wanted to, but I just don't have the time anymore and I want to focus on school because I want to go to medical school to be a surgeon. Anyways this server is sorta plain.
[b][u][size=20pt]YOU WILL NOT POST/RELEASE THE SOURCE+CLIENT THAT HAS NO ANTI-LEECH IN IT![/size][/u][/b]
[center]::Server/Client Features::[/center] Client Features -New JFrame -New Interfaces -Good Custom items -Fixed Mini-Map Glitch when you teleport. -New Magic icons -New Hit Icons -New Block Icons -New Hp Bars -Fixed Cache no more Helmets in the Fences -Added Cursors in the JFrame -New Rs Text -Custom Crowns -New Context Menus -TONSSSS Of interfaces
Server Features Xlog fixed 100% No dupes that I know of) Most fixed. Made some handlers- Hitmananger Hit.java Bountyhunter.java DialougeHandler Degradehandler Fite waves handler SKILLS Herblore.java Crafting.java Cooking.java Smithing.java You can make them work.
--REASON IT SAYS TRAGEDY PKING IS BECAUSE I USED TO CODE FOR THEM... [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa-1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaama.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaast.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaainfo.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaapestinboat-1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/aaaaaaaaaaatelleleee23.jpg[/img] You can finish the bank interface.. [IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss241/jeffey12345/bank.jpg[/img] Much more dl to see
Server Download- http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?yltj0c2zmno Client Download- http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?umm53ynywn2
Too let all you leachers know I changed all Spirit loading paths to incorrect ones, and the preloading models change the path. You can fix them. Also Errors in Class9, Error on start up Unpacking Interfaces 95. (Should know how to fix) Error in Client.java,Class8, and gui.java
Server Errors On this part [s]public void checkbhleaders[/s] and [s]public void checkrgleaders[/s]
Then some command errors, The 2 above cause the 100 errors.
1 more leech wich you can figure out.
[u]Credits[/u] Me Mitko for SPIRITS NOT A INTERFACE (Referring to DEATHSPIRIT, or whatever his name is) All the people I got Spirits from.
